The paper focuses on image analysis and retrieval, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed method involves capturing spatial relationships between image regions, which could also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The evaluation of the proposed method involves querying a large database, which could be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories.
